&lt;p&gt;作为观众, 我们的情绪也是纠结的: 既希望新剧能忠于经典(大部分人心目中的经典形象基本是87版铬下的), 又希望有新意和超越. 这二者之间本就有冲突, 平衡把握得要好才能让大部分观众满意. 既不能过度保守弄个九分相似的复刻版, 又不能一味创新弄出不伦不类的东西, 例如铜钱头.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://yongchen.org/posts/geng-zhen-shi-zi-ran-de-hong-lou-meng-dai-yu-chuan/"&gt;Read more…&lt;/a&gt; (1 min remaining to read)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><category>文学</category><category>电视</category><guid>http://yongchen.org/posts/geng-zhen-shi-zi-ran-de-hong-lou-meng-dai-yu-chuan/</guid><pubDate>Sat, 09 Jul 2016 11:23:43 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>Arc Length Reparameterization</title><link>http://yongchen.org/posts/arc-length-reparameterization/</link><dc:creator>YONG</dc:creator><description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;reference: &lt;a class="reference external" href="https://services.math.duke.edu/~wka/math103/curvature.pdf"&gt;https://services.math.duke.edu/~wka/math103/curvature.pdf&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Suppose &lt;span class="math"&gt;\(I\)&lt;/span&gt; is an interval and &lt;span class="math"&gt;\(\mathbf{r} : I \mapsto \mathbb{R}^n\)&lt;/span&gt; is a curve in &lt;span class="math"&gt;\(\mathbb{R}^n\)&lt;/span&gt; whose speed is never zero. Suppose &lt;span class="math"&gt;\(t_0 \in I\)&lt;/span&gt; and let&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="math"&gt;
\begin{equation*}
\sigma (t) = \int_{t_0}^t \| \vec{r}' (\tau) \| d\tau
\end{equation*}
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://yongchen.org/posts/arc-length-reparameterization/"&gt;Read more…&lt;/a&gt; (1 min remaining to read)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><category>algorithm</category><category>mathjax</category><guid>http://yongchen.org/posts/arc-length-reparameterization/</guid><pubDate>Tue, 28 Jun 2016 02:04:59 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>收猴子卖猴子的故事(加强版)</title><link>http://yongchen.org/posts/shou-hou-zi-mai-hou-zi-de-gu-shi-jia-qiang-ban/</link><dc:creator>YONG</dc:creator><description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;原文: &lt;a class="reference external" href="http://www.hanyang.com.tw/%e7%8c%b4%e5%ad%90%e7%9a%84%e6%95%85%e4%ba%8b-%e5%8a%a0%e5%bc%b7%e7%89%88/?variant=zh-tw"&gt;猴子的故事-加强版&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;最近网路上流传一段故事是这样说的：&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;「有一个商人到了一个山村，村子周围的山上全是猴子。商人就和村子种地的农民说，我买猴子，100元一只。村民不知是真是假，试着抓猴子，商人果然给了100元。於是全村的人都去抓猴子，这比种地合算得多了。很快商人买了两千多只猴子，山上猴子很少了。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://yongchen.org/posts/shou-hou-zi-mai-hou-zi-de-gu-shi-jia-qiang-ban/"&gt;Read more…&lt;/a&gt; (1 min remaining to read)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><category>故事</category><category>金融</category><guid>http://yongchen.org/posts/shou-hou-zi-mai-hou-zi-de-gu-shi-jia-qiang-ban/</guid><pubDate>Wed, 15 Jun 2016 07:09:52 GMT</pubDate></item></channel></rss>